name: Matthew Newcombe
text: Do not eat here. Disgusting. The hot wings taste of vinegar and the pizza sauce tastes like it has been out in the sun for 2 days. When travelling from LA to Phoenix a picnic is recommended. Remember, gross towns and gross food go together.
